> Fire|**Lesser Fire Elemental**
> Harmony|**Ancient Spirit** (any)
> Life|***Beast*** *or* ***Plant*** (any, CR 2 or below)
> Mana|**Arcane Wyrm** *or* **Lesser Arcane Elemental**
> Shadow|**Voidwalker**
